attributes.name: Biscotti | Live Resin Cart
attributes.body: Airo Brands puts the true-plant experience at the forefront with the Live Rosin Series. Live Rosin is full-spectrum, premium cannabis concentrate made from fresh-frozen cannabis plants. What makes Live Rosin different from Live Resin? Live Rosin is solventless, meaning no chemicals are used in the extraction process. It’s similar to Live Resin as it’s packed with full-spectrum cannabinoids and a robust terpene profile. The unique atomizer assembly is optimized for Live Rosin to preserve the maximum amount of terpenes. Each cartridge captures the distinctive characteristics of its strain – creating the most authentic flower-like experience in a vape. Live Rosin is extracted using all-natural processes. At the ideal plant maturity, plants are harvested and immediately frozen – which is the “live”. Then, the plants are placed in a rosin press. The press uses heat and pressure to extract a hot oil from the plants – which is the rosin. Easily find your new favorite cartridge with its distinct rose gold color. **AiroPod Cartridges are only compatible with the AiroPro and AiroSport Vaporizer.**

attributes.name: Pumpkin Pie | Distillate Cart
attributes.body: CONTROLLED EXTRACTIONREMEDIATIONDISTILLATION We achieve Molecular Perfection within our Premium Distillate products via methodologies found commonly in other industries. Much like filtered water, cooking oils and other natural plant oil products, refinement is used to isolate specific desired compounds found with the different organic starting materials. Cannabis is a complex organic plant material that contains compounds which are not considered “healthy” for ingestion or inhalation via vaporization. The predominant compounds within cannabis that interest us are called “Cannabinoids”. A plethora of data and litereture suggest that cannabinoids are beneficial to many aspects of human health. Through refinement and isolation we can offer consumers a clean way to enjoy cannabinoids without plant volatiles, waxes and fats found in pre-processed cannabis biomass materials or crude extracts. At Pharmers, we employ methods of modern chemistry to refine crude cannabis extract into a pure, cannabinoid rich, odorless, and tasteless distillate oil. Demonstrated through decades of experience in extracting and refining, our founder Don Romero, properly named “The Distillate Don”, became a trusted source of education and consultation for industry giants from coast to coast. With Don at the helm, Pharmers Quality has established itself nationally as the expert level extraction and distillation specialists. What makes our oil different? It’s simple, purity through proper processes. When enjoying Pharmers, the consumer can trust they have a safe, clean, and pure product in their hands.

Combining a Haze hybrid with a Northern Lights #5 and Shiva Skunk cross, Sensi Seeds created Jack Herer hoping to capture both cerebral elevation and heavy resin production. Its rich genetic background gives rise to several different variations of Jack Herer, each phenotype bearing its own unique features and effects. Leafly reviewers tell us that Jack Herer’s effects include feeling energetic, creative, and uplifted. However, consumers typically describe this 55% sativa hybrid as blissful, clear-headed, and creative. Jack Herer was created in the Netherlands in the mid-1990s, where it was later distributed by Dutch pharmacies as a recognized medical-grade strain. Prohibition 37 flower is our specialty and what we have built our brand on. Our production facilities include 2 state-of-the-art indoor cultivations totaling 14,000 sq ft in our home city of Albuquerque. We also have an outdoor farm in Belen, and greenhouse productions in Belen and Gallup. Our mission is to destigmatize the industry, produce outstanding quality cannabis, and positively contribute to the quality of life of our patients and customers. We currently grow over 75 cultivars, and are continually adding the newest and most sought after genetics to bring to every corner of New Mexico. WHO IS P37? Prohibition 37 is a physician-led, nationally recognized, and award-winning vertical cannabis company. P37 is highly focused on the customer experience and science of the medicinal and recreational effects of its many products. Our name is derived from The Marihuana Tax Act of 1937, which was a U.S. federal law that effectively criminalized the possession and distribution of marijuana. While it did not directly ban the cannabis plant, it imposed strict regulations and heavy taxes on its cultivation, sales, and use. This made it impossible to legally engage in these activities, leading to a de facto prohibition of cannabis. The Act played a significant role in shaping the modern approach to marijuana regulation in the United States.\ SOCIAL EQUITY AND JUSTICE The Marihuana Tax Act of 1937 disproportionately targeted minorities, particularly African, Mexican, and Jewish American communities. While the act did not explicitly mention racial or ethnic groups, its implementation and enforcement were marked by tremendous racial bias and discrimination. Law enforcement, for example, selectively targeted and arrested individuals from minority groups and used marijuana-related offenses as a pretext for discriminatory actions. This contributed to the disproportionate impact of the Act on minorities, perpetuating racial stereotypes and injustices for generations to come. Our mission at Prohibition 37 is to reverse decades of cannabis-related injustice and create a healthy, communal, and scientific approach to cannabis use.
